{
  "page": "Corso",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;font-weight:bold; background: none; line-height: 1.1em;\"><table style=\"width:100%\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:left;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/Maesters\" title=\"Maesters\"><img alt=\"Maester.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/4/46/Maester.svg/50px-Maester.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"50\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/4/46/Maester.svg/75px-Maester.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/4/46/Maester.svg/100px-Maester.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:middle;text-align:center;padding:0px 7px 5px 7px\"><span style=\"font-size:80%;font-weight:normal\"> Maester</span><br />Corso</td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:right;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/Maesters\" title=\"Maesters\"><img alt=\"Maester.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/4/46/Maester.svg/50px-Maester.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"50\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/4/46/Maester.svg/75px-Maester.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/4/46/Maester.svg/100px-Maester.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td></tr></tbody></table></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\"></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Title</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Maester\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Maester\">Maester</a> at <a href=\"/index.php/Summerhall\" title=\"Summerhall\">Summerhall</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Allegiances</th><td>\n<div class=\"plainlist\"><ul><li>The <a href=\"/index.php/Citadel\" title=\"Citadel\">Citadel</a></li><li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Targaryen\" title=\"House Targaryen\">House Targaryen</a></li></ul></div></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Died</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/259_AC\" title=\"259 AC\">259&#160;AC</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_targaryen_kings:_aegon_v.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiafthe_targaryen_kings:_aegon_v.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup><br /><a href=\"/index.php/Summerhall\" title=\"Summerhall\">Summerhall</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Book</th><td>\n<i><a href=\"/index.php/The_World_of_Ice_%26_Fire\" title=\"The World of Ice &amp; Fire\">The World of Ice &amp; Fire</a></i> (mentioned)</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>Corso</b> was the <a href=\"/index.php/Maester\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Maester\">maester</a> at <a href=\"/index.php/Summerhall\" title=\"Summerhall\">Summerhall</a> by the end of King <a href=\"/index.php/Aegon_V_Targaryen\" title=\"Aegon V Targaryen\">Aegon V Targaryen</a>'s reign.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Corso&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Corso sent a letter describing the <a href=\"/index.php/Tragedy_at_Summerhall\" title=\"Tragedy at Summerhall\">Tragedy at Summerhall</a> before his death, but a mishap led to ink blotting out much of the information:<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_targaryen_kings:_aegon_v.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiafthe_targaryen_kings:_aegon_v.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup><sup id=\"cite_ref-GyldaynRetcon_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-GyldaynRetcon-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p>the <a href=\"/index.php/House_Targaryen\" title=\"House Targaryen\">blood of the dragon</a> gathered in one …<br />… seven <a href=\"/index.php/Dragon_eggs\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Dragon eggs\">eggs</a>, to honor the <a href=\"/index.php/Faith_of_the_Seven\" title=\"Faith of the Seven\">seven gods</a>, though the <a href=\"/index.php/Aegon_V_Targaryen\" title=\"Aegon V Targaryen\">king</a>'s own <a href=\"/index.php/Septon\" title=\"Septon\">septon</a> had warned …<br />… <a href=\"/index.php/Pyromancer\" title=\"Pyromancer\">pyromancers</a> …<br />… <a href=\"/index.php/Wildfire\" title=\"Wildfire\">wild fire</a> …<br />… flames grew out of control … towering … burned so hot that …<br />… died, but for the valor of the <a href=\"/index.php/Duncan_the_Tall\" title=\"Duncan the Tall\">Lord Comman</a> …<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_targaryen_kings:_aegon_v.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiafthe_targaryen_kings:_aegon_v.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;Corso's letter</cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Behind_the_Scenes\">Behind the Scenes</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Corso&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Behind the Scenes\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Corso only appears in latest prints of <i><a href=\"/index.php/The_World_of_Ice_%26_Fire\" title=\"The World of Ice &amp; Fire\">The World of Ice &amp; Fire</a></i>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-GyldaynRetcon_2-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-GyldaynRetcon-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup> In earlier prints, his role was played by Archmaester <a href=\"/index.php/Gyldayn\" title=\"Gyldayn\">Gyldayn</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Corso&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rtwoiafthe_targaryen_kings:_aegon_v.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_targaryen_kings:_aegon_v.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">1.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_targaryen_kings:_aegon_v.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\">1.1</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_targaryen_kings:_aegon_v.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-2\">1.2</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_World_of_Ice_%26_Fire\" title=\"The World of Ice &amp; Fire\">The World of Ice &amp; Fire</a></i>, The Targaryen Kings: Aegon V.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-GyldaynRetcon-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-GyldaynRetcon_2-0\">2.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-GyldaynRetcon_2-1\">2.1</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.reddit.com/r/asoiaf/comments/eyf4bc\">When did they update The World of Ice &amp; Fire? (February 3, 2020)</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-3\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a href=\"/index.php/Errata_of_The_World_of_Ice_%26_Fire#The_Targaryen_Kings\" title=\"Errata of The World of Ice &amp; Fire\">Errata of The World of Ice &amp; Fire</a>: Aegon V.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n<table class=\"wikitable succession-box noprint\" style=\"margin:0.5em auto; font-size:small;clear:both;\">\n<tbody><tr>\n<td style=\"width: 30%; text-align: center;\" rowspan=\"